original_title: The Corps: Keepers of the Spirit
overview: “The Corps: Keepers of the Spirit” is a feature-length documentary that tells the story of The Corps, from its rich history to its bright future.  The Corps documentary captures an entire year on “The Quad” with unprecedented access to student life.  From  F.O.W. to Final Review, “The Corps:  Keepers of the Spirit” dramatically reveals the cadet training process and the leaders it builds.
tagline: There's a spirit that ne'er be told
title: The Corps: Keepers of the Spirit
